sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant HTTPSrv as caikit HTTP Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPCSrv as caikit gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Gateway as REST Gateway<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Module as caikit_nlp Module<br/>(in-process)
    participant PyTorch as PyTorch Model<br/>(in-process)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>gRPC (configurable port)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Client,PyTorch: Flow 1: Local Model Inference
        Client->>HTTPSrv: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTP (configurable TLS)
        HTTPSrv->>Module: Function call (in-process)<br/>TextGeneration / EmbeddingModule
        Module->>PyTorch: Forward pass<br/>torch.no_grad()
        PyTorch-->>Module: Tensor output
        Module-->>HTTPSrv: Formatted response
        HTTPSrv-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: TGIS Remote Inference
        Client->>GRPCSrv: gRPC TextGeneration.Generate<br/>8085/TCP (configurable TLS)
        GRPCSrv->>Module: Function call (in-process)<br/>TextGenerationTGIS / PeftPromptTuningTGIS
        Module->>TGIS: gRPC Generate / GenerateStream<br/>Configurable TLS/mTLS
        TGIS-->>Module: GenerationResponse / stream
        Module-->>GRPCSrv: Formatted response
        GRPCSrv-->>Client: gRPC Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,FS: Flow 3: PEFT Prompt Tuning Training
        Client->>GRPCSrv: gRPC Train request<br/>8085/TCP (configurable TLS)
        GRPCSrv->>Module: PeftPromptTuning.train()
        Module->>HFHub: Download base model<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>HF Token (optional)
        HFHub-->>Module: Model artifacts
        Note over Module: PEFT prompt tuning<br/>with Accelerate + FSDP
        Module->>FS: Save tuned model<br/>File I/O
        Module-->>GRPCSrv: Training result
        GRPCSrv-->>Client: Training response
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Client,GRPCSrv: Flow 4: Multi-Process Gateway Runtime
        Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/*<br/>HTTP/8080 (no TLS)
        Gateway->>GRPCSrv: Forward via gRPC<br/>8085/TCP (configurable TLS)
        GRPCSrv->>Module: Function call (in-process)
        Module-->>GRPCSrv: Response
        GRPCSrv-->>Gateway: gRPC Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
    end
